1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 24=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Then We'll Go to Hell Together)

4
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:54,880
Your Highness honors us
with your presence.

5
00:00:55,280 --> 00:00:57,480
How may we serve you?

6
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:07,080
Qingqing.

7
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,240
I've come today

8
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,960
to deliver two imperial decrees

9
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:16,560
to you and the Pan family.

10
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,320
Please sit and listen.

11
00:01:38,680 --> 00:01:40,800
By the Mandate of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

12
00:01:41,160 --> 00:01:42,960
Pan Yang's conduct
has been found wanting,

13
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:44,390
making him unworthy of Li Qingqing.

14
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,280
Their marriage is hereby dissolved,

15
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:47,480
effective immediately.

16
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,760
From this day on,

17
00:01:48,770 --> 00:01:49,880
they shall have no ties to each other.

18
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:50,400
This...

19
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,320
Your Highness...

20
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,040
Continue.

21
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,560
Li Qingqing,

22
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,800
gentle and virtuous,

23
00:01:55,810 --> 00:01:58,590
is destined by heaven to be the Crown Prince
Zheng Yuanzhao's consort.

24
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,720
She is hereby bestowed
the title of Crown Princess.

25
00:02:00,730 --> 00:02:02,560
A favorable date
shall be chosen for the wedding.

26
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,800
By imperial decree.

27
00:02:06,790 --> 00:02:08,400
Zheng Yuanzhao, have you lost your mind?

28
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,360
Your Highness,

29
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:14,360
Qingqing is the Pan family's
daughter-in-law.

30
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,920
You can't force her to marry...

31
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,160
Did you all forget

32
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,760
how that jerk Pan Yang

33
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,200
humiliated Miss Qingqing?

34
00:02:20,210 --> 00:02:22,590
And yet you still have the nerve
to call her part of your family?

35
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,120
Heaven is my witness.

36
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,680
We've never mistreated Qingqing.

37
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,040
We've even been making
Yang apologize to her.

38
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,680
Mom, stay out of this.

39
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,760
Your Highness,

40
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:36,000
I'm not worthy

41
00:02:36,480 --> 00:02:37,840
of Qingqing.

42
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,280
I'll divorce her.

43
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,320
Yes, exactly.

44
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:43,200
My sister's talent
in business is unmatched.

45
00:02:43,320 --> 00:02:45,040
She's the perfect match
for Your Highness.

46
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,720
You ungrateful fool!

47
00:02:49,120 --> 00:02:52,040
Qingqing is your lawfully wedded wife!

48
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,600
Wife or not,

49
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,240
if Your Highness wants her,

50
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:57,760
the entire Pan family
will gladly pledge our loyalty.

51
00:02:58,040 --> 00:03:00,280
You worthless...

52
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,240
Master!

53
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:02,840
Master!

54
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:04,800
Dad!

55
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:05,200
Dad!

56
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:06,200
Help him inside to rest.

57
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:10,760
What are you doing?

58
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:11,760
Let go!

59
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,830
The marriage contract
between you and the Pan family

60
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,200
was arranged by them.

61
00:03:15,760 --> 00:03:17,240
So the divorce papers

62
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:19,480
must naturally
bear their fingerprints as proof.

63
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,240
No.

64
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,880
I... I won't sign it.

65
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,200
Qingqing isn't just my daughter-in-law.

66
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,840
She's my daughter.

67
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,880
I won't.

68
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,160
I won't sign it.

69
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,600
Beautiful lady...

70
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:31,920
I won't sign it!

71
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,280
Mom, stay out of this.

72
00:03:34,040 --> 00:03:34,720
Mom!

73
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,880
Yang...

74
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:36,560
Beautiful lady...

75
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:37,480
Mom!

76
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:38,560
My lady!

77
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,640
Zheng Yuanzhao,
what are you trying to do?

78
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,520
Put your fingerprint on it.

79
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:45,480
Bah! I won't!

80
00:03:47,600 --> 00:03:48,400
Dad!

81
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:50,560
Dad!

82
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:53,560
Let go!

83
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,560
Dad!

84
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:57,160
Pan Yang!

85
00:03:57,720 --> 00:03:58,760
Those are your parents!

86
00:03:58,760 --> 00:03:59,960
And you're just going to stand there?

87
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,000
Are you even human?

88
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:04,200
Your Highness...

89
00:04:04,200 --> 00:04:05,320
Please show mercy.

90
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:16,700
(Divorce Agreement)

91
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,160
Zheng Yuanzhao,

92
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,960
this is between you and me.

93
00:04:21,960 --> 00:04:24,120
If you're a real man, let them go.

94
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,840
Li Qingqing,

95
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:28,240
if you dare defy me again,

96
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:30,800
it won't just be those two
old fools from the Pan family.

97
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,400
You'll never see

98
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:34,040
Caiyuan or Jiuzhu again.

99
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,600
So it really was you behind the attack.

100
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:40,480
I must have been blind

101
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,920
not to see the ambition you were hiding.

102
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:45,680
People change.

103
00:04:47,440 --> 00:04:48,600
Especially

104
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:50,700
when the only way to get what they want

105
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:54,280
is by using whatever means necessary.

106
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,040
Get yourself ready.

107
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,800
I can't wait

108
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:02,200
to see you in your bridal gown.

109
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:12,280
Dad!

110
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:13,680
Beautiful lady!

111
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,760
Beautiful lady!

112
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:17,360
Dad!

113
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:19,560
Dad!

114
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:20,880
Dad!

115
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,320
Dad!

116
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,520
Where is he?

117
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,320
Why is he running off?

118
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,560
One's biting at my heels,

119
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,000
and the other's nothing but trouble.

120
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,560
Those two brothers
are trying to drive me crazy.

121
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,560
I'm

122
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,160
done for.

123
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,560
No.

124
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:04,880
Calm down.

125
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,520
Calm down.

126
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:12,280
Zheng Yuanzhao took Jiuzhu and Caiyuan

127
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,360
to use them as leverage against me.

128
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:17,040
That means they won't kill them for now.

129
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,200
What I need to do now

130
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,640
is figure out how to deal with him.

131
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,520
How?

132
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:25,240
How?

133
00:06:26,080 --> 00:06:27,240
How?

134
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,760
Gunpowder.

135
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,000
Your Highness,

136
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:39,200
I knew you'd be safe.

137
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:46,160
How far has Zheng Yuanzhao gotten?

138
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:47,800
Ever since His Majesty fell gravely ill,

139
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:50,080
the Second Prince
has taken control of the court.

140
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,720
He's even publicly branded you
as the rebel behind Wangshi Tower

141
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:54,180
and sent men everywhere
to hunt you down.

142
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:56,280
Birds of a feather flock together.

143
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,320
The ones he's won over

144
00:06:58,320 --> 00:07:00,480
are nothing but useless fools.

145
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,760
Issue my order.

146
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,280
Recall the Northern Army at once

147
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,040
and contact our men within the ranks.

148
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,760
Before he can react,

149
00:07:10,640 --> 00:07:12,680
I'll march into the capital.

150
00:07:13,080 --> 00:07:13,600
Yes,

151
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,120
Your Highness.

152
00:07:16,380 --> 00:07:18,400
Li Qingqing is the Tower Master
of Wangshi Tower.

153
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,860
How do you intend to deal with her?

154
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:29,640
Whatever she did to me,

155
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,520
I'll repay

156
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:36,600
every bit of it.

157
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,680
Chou, why are you here?

158
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,640
Didn't I tell you it's dangerous outside
these past few days

159
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,240
and not to wander around?

160
00:07:54,400 --> 00:07:55,640
Chou?

161
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,400
Only now

162
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,800
do I realize

163
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,240
you've always
thought I was so easy to fool,

164
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,800
and so easy to push around.

165
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,000
I...

166
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:14,160
You want to run?

167
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,280
Too late.

168
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:22,720
Go on.

169
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,520
Why did you stop running?

170
00:08:32,280 --> 00:08:33,320
Master.

171
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:35,440
I...

172
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:37,280
When you shot me at the cliff,

173
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,720
you didn't hesitate at all.

174
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:39,680
No...

175
00:08:39,680 --> 00:08:41,640
When you ordered me around like a dog,

176
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:43,000
weren't you enjoying yourself?

177
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:45,600
Is that how you saw me?

178
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:48,160
Like I was nothing but a joke?

179
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:50,000
Just calm down first.

180
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:51,000
Let me explain...

181
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,600
Explain?

182
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,360
Explain what?

183
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,120
How you used me?

184
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,600
How you deceived me?

185
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,400
Li Qingqing,

186
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,920
I really want to cut your heart out

187
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,960
and see if it's black inside.

188
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,240
I trusted you.

189
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,360
I trusted that you weren't
the Tower Master

190
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,760
and that you'd never hurt me.

191
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:13,000
Yet you joined forces
with Zheng Yuanzhao.

192
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:15,880
Is this how you repay my trust?

193
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,560
Can you at least be reasonable?

194
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,280
Who's the one ruining whose life?

195
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:25,480
My Wangshi Tower,

196
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:28,070
my bank, and my newspaper office
were all destroyed because of you.

197
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:30,000
I'm the biggest victim here.

198
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:31,200
And Zheng Yuanzhao?

199
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,440
Who joined forces with him?

200
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,400
We were just business partners.

201
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,680
I...

202
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:39,600
I just wanted to make some money.

203
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:44,040
I just wanted to make some money,

204
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:47,000
retire early, and live a good life.

205
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,000
Was that so wrong?

206
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,160
The two of you keep chasing me around,

207
00:09:52,160 --> 00:09:53,960
acting like you won't stop
until I'm dead.

208
00:09:54,080 --> 00:09:56,400
What did I ever do to deserve this?

209
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:02,240
Every time I finally manage
to make a little money,

210
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,160
it's gone.

211
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,040
I make a little money,

212
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:05,280
and it's gone again.

213
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:11,080
How is that any different
from being tortured to death?

214
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,000
Why are you crying?

215
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,720
I haven't even done anything yet.

216
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:20,240
Don't think your tears
will get you out of this.

217
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,960
I know better than anyone

218
00:10:25,760 --> 00:10:27,320
how good you are at putting on an act.

219
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,680
I'm not acting.

220
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:35,120
I'm telling you the truth.

221
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,000
I need you.

222
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,480
You need me?

223
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,400
Zheng Yuanzhao
is forcing me to marry him.

224
00:10:44,400 --> 00:10:46,400
He wants to take over everything I own.

225
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,680
You're the Crown Prince.

226
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:50,430
You're the only one
who can stand against him.

227
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,200
We're in this together.

228
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:58,840
This is gunpowder.

229
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:01,320
With this, we can
take Zheng Yuanzhao down.

230
00:11:01,960 --> 00:11:03,000
Let's work together.

231
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,080
If you defeat him,

232
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,360
then whether you kill me or punish me,

233
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,320
I'll accept it.

234
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,680
(Zheng Yuanhe...)

235
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:22,160
(You're hopeless.)

236
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,360
(I actually thought there was)

237
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:26,800
(even the slightest place
for you in her heart.)

238
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:28,880
That's right.

239
00:11:31,560 --> 00:11:33,000
I almost forgot.

240
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,920
You still need me.

241
00:11:38,880 --> 00:11:40,520
I...

242
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,880
But to me,

243
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:45,400
you're no longer of any use.

244
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:48,400
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

245
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:51,820
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

246
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:54,960
I'm already in your hands anyway.

247
00:11:55,060 --> 00:11:56,500
If you want to kill me, then do it.

248
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,960
Whoever's afraid is a coward.

249
00:12:00,790 --> 00:12:02,550
♪Though fate tries♪

250
00:12:02,780 --> 00:12:05,370
♪To make us pass each other by♪

251
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:08,880
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

252
00:12:09,290 --> 00:12:10,940
♪Though time slips by♪

253
00:12:10,940 --> 00:12:12,610
♪As day turns into night♪

254
00:12:13,210 --> 00:12:17,200
♪I still remember our days
at Wangshi Tower♪

255
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:19,990
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

256
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:21,650
♪Blessed by fate♪

257
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:26,430
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

258
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,230
♪Your smiling face♪

259
00:12:29,230 --> 00:12:32,220
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

260
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:35,710
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

261
00:12:36,410 --> 00:12:39,510
♪And wander the world together♪

262
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:41,200
Zheng Yuanhe, you jerk!

263
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,440
This time,

264
00:12:44,200 --> 00:12:45,640
I'll let you go.

265
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:49,600
But if you ever deceive me again,

266
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:52,210
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

267
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:55,160
I'll drag you down to hell with me.

268
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:57,800
Do you understand?

269
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:04,070
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

270
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:18,230
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

271
00:13:18,990 --> 00:13:22,370
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

272
00:13:23,140 --> 00:13:24,880
♪Your smile♪

273
00:13:25,140 --> 00:13:27,430
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

274
00:13:27,430 --> 00:13:31,110
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

275
00:13:31,570 --> 00:13:34,880
♪Yet I stand before you♪

276
00:13:35,620 --> 00:13:39,450
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

277
00:13:39,870 --> 00:13:41,790
♪Though fate tries♪

278
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:44,370
♪To make us pass each other by♪

279
00:13:44,590 --> 00:13:48,010
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

280
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,900
♪Though time slips by♪

281
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:51,660
♪As day turns into night♪

282
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:56,200
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

283
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:59,000
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

284
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,790
♪Blessed by fate♪

285
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:05,950
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

286
00:14:05,950 --> 00:14:08,390
♪Your smiling face♪

287
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:11,230
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

288
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:14,850
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

289
00:14:15,370 --> 00:14:18,830
♪And wander the world together♪

290
00:14:18,830 --> 00:14:20,170
♪Holding you close♪

291
00:14:20,170 --> 00:14:22,710
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

292
00:14:22,710 --> 00:14:25,030
♪Your tenderness♪

293
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:27,890
♪Is the brightest moon♪

294
00:14:27,890 --> 00:14:31,590
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

295
00:14:32,110 --> 00:14:35,400
♪Our love will never fade away♪

296
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,860
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

297
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:42,640
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

